summary:
Senior expert in audit, consulting and finance with diverse cross-industry experience across telecoms, transportation & consumer products
• Demonstrates ability to executes critical decisions related to;
o Risk assessment
o Implementation of procedures to reach desired level of assurance
o Evaluation of evidence.
• Experienced in providing consulting services for development accounting policies in accordance with IFRS for Group reporting
• A proactive approach and the ability to work autonomously and as part of a team
• Expert knowledge of IFRS accounting principles and reporting
• Extensive experience within both an Internal and External audit environment
• Experienced in Test IT-related controls under SOX requirements
• Experienced in Data Analytic tools and procedures
• Knowledgeable in complex ERP (SAP) and billing systems
• Experienced in Microsoft office tools (Excel, Word, Power Point, Project)
• Skilled in client-facing communication with the ability to discuss issues and make recommendations
• Good team leader with diverse coaching experience - managing teams of between 3–5 professionals
